headline: Amcor Meets Earnings Estimates in Q3, Closes Berry Global Merger
summary: AMCR's fiscal Q3 results reflect flat y/y volumes and unfavorable foreign currency impact. It expects 12% EPS accretion in FY26 from the Berry Global merger.
